## âœ¨ Features

### ğŸ“‹ Module 1: AI-Powered Smart Survey Tool
- ğŸ” **Real-time Data Validation** - Instant error detection and correction
- ğŸ§  **Adaptive Questioning** - ML-driven dynamic survey logic 
- ğŸ“± **Offline Capability** - Seamless synchronization when connectivity restored
- ğŸ“ **Geolocation Tagging** - GPS coordinates and timestamp verification
- ğŸŒ **Multilingual Support** - English and Hindi interface with voice-to-text

### âš™ï¸ Module 2: Automated Data Preparation & Reporting Engine  
- ğŸ¤– **Automated Data Cleaning** - ML-powered outlier detection and imputation
- ğŸ“Š **Statistical Estimation** - Complex sampling weights and variance calculation
- ğŸ“ **Natural Language Reports** - AI-generated narratives using GPT models
- ğŸ“ˆ **Dynamic Visualizations** - Automated chart and table generation
- ğŸ¯ **Small Area Estimation** - Granular insights for specific demographics

### ğŸ”Œ Module 3: Intelligent Data API Gateway
- ğŸ’¬ **Natural Language to SQL** - Plain English queries converted to database operations
- ğŸ“‹ **Standardized JSON Output** - Machine-readable format for all responses
- ğŸ” **Secure & Scalable** - JWT authentication with role-based access control
- ğŸ“š **Metadata Integration** - Comprehensive data dictionary and lineage tracking
- ğŸ”„ **Version Control** - Historical dataset access and reproducibility

