| Data Source | URL | Description | Status |
|-------------|-----|-------------|--------|
| ğŸ›ï¸ **MoSPI API** | `api.mospi.gov.in` | Consumer Price Index, Inflation Data | âœ… Live |
| ğŸ“Š **eSankhyiki Portal** | `esankhyiki.mospi.gov.in` | NSS, ASI, Economic Census (135M+ records) | âœ… Live |
| ğŸ“š **National Data Archive** | `microdata.gov.in` | 178+ NSSO surveys and microdata | âœ… Live |
| ğŸŒ **Open Government Data** | `data.gov.in` | Various government datasets | âœ… Live |

### ğŸ”— Integration Features

- **Real-time synchronization** every 15 seconds
- **Automatic failover** during API downtime  
- **Data quality validation** against official sources
- **Rate limiting compliance** with government APIs

